Replying to the reviewer that rated this movie a 1 star because it is included in season 4--this is really unfair. Yes this movie is included in season 4 but it is most definitely not a 1 star movie. Actually, it's very good. And I'm sure that any Ben 10 fan will agree with me. If you don't own season 4 of Ben 10, this is a good investment. If you do own season 4 of Ben 10, you already have this movie (in 4 versions no less), this is not a good investment for you.
While my kids love Ban 10, this movie is included in the season 4 DVD.
